<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFJuin_Jei_Liou_and_Jiann_S._Yuan1998">Juin Jei Liou and Jiann S. Yuan (1998). <i><a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=y343FTN1TU0C&amp;pg=PA166&amp;dq=charge-controlled+bjt+physics&amp;as_brr=0&amp;ei=l9viRqilEIjopQL_i6WFDg&amp;sig=vXciSaFRmNUmg3KIhmBX7DCiVOA" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=y343FTN1TU0C&amp;pg=PA166&amp;dq=charge-controlled+bjt+physics&amp;as_brr=0&amp;ei=l9viRqilEIjopQL_i6WFDg&amp;sig=vXciSaFRmNUmg3KIhmBX7DCiVOA" rel="nofollow">Semiconductor Device Physics and Simulation</a></i>. Springer. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0306457245" class="internal">ISBN 0306457245</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=y343FTN1TU0C&amp;pg=PA166&amp;dq=charge-controlled+bjt+physics&amp;as_brr=0&amp;ei=l9viRqilEIjopQL_i6WFDg&amp;sig=vXciSaFRmNUmg3KIhmBX7DCiVOA" class="external free" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=y343FTN1TU0C&amp;pg=PA166&amp;dq=charge-controlled+bjt+physics&amp;as_brr=0&amp;ei=l9viRqilEIjopQL_i6WFDg&amp;sig=vXciSaFRmNUmg3KIhmBX7DCiVOA" rel="nofollow">http://books.google.com/books?id=y343FTN1TU0C&amp;pg=PA166&amp;dq=charge-controlled+bjt+physics&amp;as_brr=0&amp;ei=l9viRqilEIjopQL_i6WFDg&amp;sig=vXciSaFRmNUmg3KIhmBX7DCiVOA</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Semiconductor+Device+Physics+and+Simulation&amp;rft.aulast=Juin+Jei+Liou+and+Jiann+S.+Yuan&amp;rft.au=Juin+Jei+Liou+and+Jiann+S.+Yuan&amp;rft.date=1998&amp;rft.pub=Springer&amp;rft.isbn=0306457245&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3Dy343FTN1TU0C%26pg%3DPA166%26dq%3Dcharge-controlled%2Bbjt%2Bphysics%26as_brr%3D0%26ei%3Dl9viRqilEIjopQL_i6WFDg%26sig%3DvXciSaFRmNUmg3KIhmBX7DCiVOA&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Bipolar_junction_transistor"><span style="display: none